{
  "wireMagic": "pb3",
  "pens": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wsWinStyles": [ {
  
  } ],
  "wpWinPositions": [ {
  
  } ],
  "events": [ {
    "tStartMs": 360,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think back to when I\nfirst started learning coding,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3660,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I was the kid that sat in the back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 5730,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of math class in middle school,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7290,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I had my little TI-83 Plus calculator."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 10170,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we just program it with BASIC,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12600,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause at some point I realized"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14250,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I can actually program the answers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16800,
    "dDurationMs": 2350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for the math test into the calculator ."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 24783,
    "dDurationMs": 1197,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Hey, I'm Alex."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 25980,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I lead Claude Relations here at Anthropic."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 28140,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Today we're gonna be\ntalking about Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 30030,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the future of software engineering."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 31860,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I'm joined by my colleague Boris."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 33990,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I'm Boris."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 34823,
    "dDurationMs": 2317,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm a member of technical\nstaff here at Anthropic"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 37140,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and creator of Claude Code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 39000,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- A lot has happened\nin the past 12 months,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 40920,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and things are moving very, very fast,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 42750,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially in the coding domain."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 44940,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "For folks that, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 46800,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe aren't following\nthe news every single day"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 48840,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or even staying on top of the latest,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 50280,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I have trouble myself sometimes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 52440,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "can you kind of catch us\nup here on what's happened,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 55230,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and where are we standing currently?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 57030,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, a year ago coding\nwas totally different"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 60060,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than what it is today."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 62010,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A year ago, if you want to write code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 64590,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have a IDE,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 65610,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have some sort of\nautocomplete in the IDE,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 68220,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then there's some sort of chat app,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 69960,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you might like copy and paste code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 71700,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "back and forth a little bit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 73530,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And that was the state of the\nart, that was AI in coding."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 77610,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think maybe\nsometime around a year ago"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 80580,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we started to see agents appear"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 82710,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as a thing that people\nearnestly use in coding."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 85350,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's like a part of the workflow."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 87060,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's not like a gimmick or a prototype."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 89670,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's actually part of the inner\nloop when you're doing dev."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 92580,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think this is the thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 94050,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's changed the most in the last year,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 96600,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is now when you code, you use an agent,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 100170,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you don't directly manipulate\ntext in an IDE anymore."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 103290,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's not just about tab;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 105030,
    "dDurationMs": 2253,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's about the model writing code for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 108120,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think what we've started to see"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 109830,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is the shift from directly\nmanipulating texts"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 113160,
    "dDurationMs": 4050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to having the model do the\ntext manipulation for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 117210,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think projecting it out,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 118830,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this is sort of the\ntrajectory that we're on,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 121110,
    "dDurationMs": 2373,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is this continuing into the future."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 124320,
    "dDurationMs": 1930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I see, so we've gone from"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 127860,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it all being within a web app"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 129210,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you're copy and pasting the code out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 131010,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you're making like very\ntargeted edits, almost,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 133590,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to just being a lot more hands-off"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 135990,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and telling an agent\nwhat you want it to do,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 138510,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then trusting it to\ngo make tons of edits"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 141060,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and create whole apps\nsometimes even by itself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 143610,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 144690,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this was something that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 147390,
    "dDurationMs": 3030,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think the reason we\ncouldn't do it a year ago,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 150420,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, you know, like, people\nhave tried to make AI do coding"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 153000,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for the longest time and to, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 154830,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just like automate more and\nmore of coding in various ways."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 157200,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it hasn't really worked, I think,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 158880,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "probably for a couple of reasons:"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 159870,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "one is the models weren't\nreally good enough,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 162510,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the second one is\nthat like the scaffolding,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 164490,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the thing on top of the\nmodel, wasn't good enough."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 167610,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And when we initially\nlaunched Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 169860,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the very, very first\nversions late last year,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 172770,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think it was still using Sonnet 3.5."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 175680,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This wasn't even 3.6,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 177840,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or whatever we call this thing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 179730,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the new Sonnet 3.5."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 180750,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, upgraded Sonnet."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 182280,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah. It wasn't even this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 183750,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it like sort of worked, you know?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 185280,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, I used it for maybe 10% of my code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 187620,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or something like that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 188670,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But even then, I remember\nwhen we launched it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 191550,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we gave it to the core team."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 193200,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it was just me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 194130,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and like a few other people\non the team at the time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 196380,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I remember walking in one morning,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 198660,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and kind of on the way to to my desk,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 201210,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there was a few engineers sitting there;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 202530,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and one of them was Robert,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 203760,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and there was a couple of other engineers."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 205800,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I just walked in,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 207180,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I saw Claude Code on\ntheir screen the first time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 209730,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And like I just gave this\nto them the day before"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 212040,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and they're already using it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 213510,
    "dDurationMs": 957,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it was just the craziest thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 214467,
    "dDurationMs": 1473,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the model wasn't very good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 215940,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The harness wasn't very good."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 217110,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But even in this early version,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 219330,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it was already a little bit useful."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 221400,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think that over the last year"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 223470,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what's happened is the\nmodel has gotten way better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 226200,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at agentic coding,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 227670,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's happened with like\n3.7 and now 4.0 and Opus 4.1."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 233130,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the harness has also\ngotten a lot better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 235860,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And, you know, obviously\nthe harness is Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 237840,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because the way you\ninteract with the model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 240270,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can't just like\ndirectly use the model:"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 241740,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have to use a harness."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 242940,
    "dDurationMs": 903,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's sort of like, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 243843,
    "dDurationMs": 2427,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like if you're riding a horse,\nyou need some sort of saddle."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 246270,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And like that saddle\nmakes a giant difference"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 248400,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when you're riding a horse."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 250530,
    "dDurationMs": 985,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm not a horse rider."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 253290,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I like that analogy, though."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 254610,
    "dDurationMs": 4140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean, it is kind of\nlike Claude is the horse,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 258750,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and as the engineer you're trying to"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 261630,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "get it to go in a certain direction"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 263010,
    "dDurationMs": 870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you're trying to guide it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 263880,
    "dDurationMs": 3630,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and like you need some sort\nof scaffolding around it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 267510,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be able to steer it correctly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 270120,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the harness in this case,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 272040,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just so we're on the same page,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 273480,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is everything from like\nthe tools we're giving it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 276390,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to how we handle like the\ncontext and everything"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 279060,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for the model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 279893,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Exactly, exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 280726,
    "dDurationMs": 1034,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's like all of Claude Code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 281760,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, the model is the\nthing behind the API,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 284010,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then Claude Code,\nit's the system prompt,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 286920,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's context management,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 288330,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's tools, it's the\nability for, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 291540,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to plug in MCP servers,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 293760,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "settings, permissions,\nall this kind of stuff."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 295890,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "All of this interfaces with the model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 298140,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the model sees all the context,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 300210,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "all the output from this stuff,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 301260,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it makes a giant difference\nin the way that it performs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 303810,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think over the last year"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 305070,
    "dDurationMs": 3810,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we've learned how exactly\nwe build for the model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 308880,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the model has kind of coevolved"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 311550,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with not just Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 313290,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but all these different products"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 314640,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are using Anthropic models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 316980,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to build agentic coding tools."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 319500,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Maybe let's speak more on that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 320760,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you say coevolve,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 322530,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that because it's\nlike a deliberate thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 324600,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in which we're doing with the training, or"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 327630,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how is the model also getting better"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 329790,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at these sorts of things?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 330623,
    "dDurationMs": 2167,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as we make the product\nfeatures itself better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 332790,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- It's pretty organic, honestly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 334200,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, you know, at Anthropic,\neveryone uses Claude Code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 337320,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And that includes the researchers."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 339810,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so every day the\npeople building the models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 342120,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are using the model in\norder to do their job."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 345720,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think as part of that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 346830,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you kind of see these natural limits"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 348720,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you hit with a model."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 350520,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So, you know, as an example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 352290,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe the model's really bad"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 354030,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "at doing certain kinds of edits."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 355440,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And sometimes when you use Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 356760,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you see like, oh, failed\nto replace string,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 358380,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "failed to replace string."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 359850,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, this is a model capability,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 361200,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we can improve this\nif we learn from it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 363540,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or another example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 364800,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe something like higher level"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 366030,
    "dDurationMs": 4020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is if you just let the model\ncook for like 30 minutes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 370050,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with 3.5, it could kind\nof do it for a little bit,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 373230,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe for like a minute or\nsomething it would stay on track."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 376590,
    "dDurationMs": 1310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then with newer models"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 377900,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it kind of gets longer and longer"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 380700,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this amount of time the model\ncan operate autonomously."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 384150,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think this is really\nbased on experience,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 385830,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because you use the model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 387750,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you kind of see where as a human"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 388980,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you have to course correct and steer it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 390420,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then we've learn from that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 391253,
    "dDurationMs": 2377,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and we can kind of incorporate\nthat into the model"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 393630,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and teach it better to do this itself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 396210,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- When you're evaluating a new model,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 399000,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "do you kind of have a vibe\ncheck set of tests that you run?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 403110,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or if it's like a new feature\nthat we're rolling out"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 404880,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to make something better in the harness,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 406950,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how do you personally evaluate"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 408780,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if the performance is getting better?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 411210,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I just do my work that day."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 412830,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Interesting.\n- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 414450,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, my perfect day is\nI'm just coding all day."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 417750,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And, you know, whatever the model is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 420240,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whatever is the new thing we're testing,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 421380,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'll just code using that\nand see what the pipe is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 423690,
    "dDurationMs": 1757,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There isn't like a specific thing I do."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 425447,
    "dDurationMs": 2713,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, you just see how\ndoes it actually work for me"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 428160,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in my day to day?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 429150,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah. Exactly, exactly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 430500,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And, you know, like in day-to-day work"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 432180,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you do all sorts of stuff."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 433320,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, you're writing new code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 435120,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you're maybe like fixing bugs,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 436590,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you're maybe reading Slack messages"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 438810,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or GitHub issues to respond to feedback."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 441300,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think more and more"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 442230,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the model is able to do\nmore and more of this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 444360,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So actually, in a way, if\nyou had maybe one thing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 447420,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you always use the model for,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 448590,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you would miss out on some\nof these newer capabilities,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 451110,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like pulling in context through MCP,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 452730,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like reading your Slack messages."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 454620,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or, you know, automatically\ndebugging stuff,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 456870,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause you can pull in\nSentry logs automatically."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 459480,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, so the best eval in some sense"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 461940,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is the one that most looks like real life."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 464430,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And in that case, just using it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 466650,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "gives you the best result."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 468000,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- We tried really hard,\nwhen building Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 470490,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to build a product evals."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 472260,
    "dDurationMs": 870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 473130,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- You know, just like to\nhave some sort of benchmark;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 475110,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like, when we change a\nsystem prompt or whatever,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 477540,
    "dDurationMs": 900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is the model getting better?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 478440,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we have a little bit of this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 480060,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but honestly it's just like\nso hard to build evals."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 482940,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And by far the biggest\nsignal is just the vibes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 485850,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, does it feel smarter?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 487380,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'Cause there's such a broad\nrange of tasks they use it for."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 490080,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, that's actually a question"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 491280,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I hear from developers all the time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 493020,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is they would appreciate more guidance on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 495960,
    "dDurationMs": 3513,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how we go about prompt\ntesting and iterating."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 501270,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I know for different products"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 502530,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we have like various sorts of evals"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 503760,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we've tried to create,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 504990,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but for Claude Code it really is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 506370,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just kind of this tight feedback loop"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 508230,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that almost gives us like\nmore immediate signal"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 510240,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than any hardcoded set of evals."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 513210,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I wonder if people kind of want to hear"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 514620,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a better answer from an AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 517308,
    "dDurationMs": 2052,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But yeah, man, it's all vibes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 519360,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think at this point we're, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 521190,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the models are doing so good\non evals, like SWE-bench."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 523920,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, we're just trying\nto find these harder evals."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 526260,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And now there's like T-bench,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 527610,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is like a little bit\nless kind of saturated."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 530250,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But I think it's just really\nhard to find synthetic evals"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 532710,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that capture all the complexity\nin software engineering."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 534750,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, right."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 536100,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Do you think there's something we did"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 538230,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "uniquely to set up that\nfeedback loop internally?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 541560,
    "dDurationMs": 2490,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'Cause I feel like Claude\nCode has like the best"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 544050,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "dogfooding cycle I've seen\nof like any type of product."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 547890,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Initially, I built it the way\nthat I do any other product,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 551790,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is just listen to users"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 553980,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and make it as easy as\npossible to listen to users."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 557190,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think one part of it"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 558150,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is when we built Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 560070,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there was just like a single\nfeedback channel in Slack."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 562590,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And anytime anyone had feedback,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 563970,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I would just direct them to that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 565380,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just be like, \"Yeah, post there.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 566880,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I feel like people hesitated\nsometimes a little bit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 569790,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'Cause sometimes when you give feedback,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 572430,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you expect that no one listens"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 574800,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it kind of goes into this\nblack hole, like into a void."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 577710,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think one of the things\nthat we did really right was,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 579870,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from the beginning, whenever\nsomeone gave feedback,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 582120,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I would try to fix it as fast as I can."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 584400,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And sometimes I would\nkind of go into the office"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 586200,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then just spend like three hours"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 587580,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or two hours or whatever,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 588810,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just go through as many bugs as I can"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 590460,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and fix them as fast as I can,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 592050,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then every time comment\nback and tell people it's fixed."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 595020,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this kind of encourages\nthem to keep giving feedback."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 597720,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And to this day the Claude Code\nfeedback channel internally"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 600600,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is just this fire hose, just nonstop."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 602760,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Oh, totally."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 603593,
    "dDurationMs": 3307,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I remember, on those\nearly days, and still do,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 606900,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "dropping in there, posting something,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 608430,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and immediately your emoji reacting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 610650,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or you're asking for more\nclarification and more questions,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 614070,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you do feel like, oh, okay,\nmy feedback's being heard."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 617430,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then you're able to like actually be,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 619650,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, incentivized"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 620880,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to go post more feedback in the future."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 623280,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, 'cause, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 624540,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "honestly, like, I don't\nknow what I'm doing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 625740,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, no one really knows\nwhat they're doing with AI."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 627810,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, we're kind of discovering\nthis thing as we build it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 630480,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the best indicator\nis what the users want."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 633600,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So you gotta listen."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 634710,
    "dDurationMs": 1743,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, switching gears slightly,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 638070,
    "dDurationMs": 2950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what is like the current state\nof Claude Code as a product?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 642000,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What are the latest features?\nWhat are you excited about?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 645420,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Some things that you're seeing\nfolks do with it right now?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 647940,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Claude Code, from the start,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 649050,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was built to be the simplest thing it can"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 651000,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and to be as hackable as possible."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 653580,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think the hackability is something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 655260,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that we've been developing a lot,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 657030,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and that's something I'm\nreally excited about."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 659640,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So originally, the way to hack Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 661920,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is adding to its CLAUDE.md."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 664650,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That was the original extension point."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 666600,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And CLAUDE.md, as you\nknow, is like this file."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 669000,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You can put it in the root directory,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 671100,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can put it in child directories."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 672450,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's kind of different\nplaces you can put it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 674310,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it's just additional\ncontext to give Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 677070,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it kind of goes with your repo."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 678390,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You often check it into your code base."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 680400,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it's kind of, you know,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 681600,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a little bit more\ninformation about the code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 683820,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But over time we've added a\nlot more extension points."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 686070,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So now there's a very\nsophisticated setting system"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 688650,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and permission system."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 690750,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's hooks now which Dixon built."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 694650,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Dixon's an engineer on our team,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 696000,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and he just kind of saw all\nthese different user asks"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 698430,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "coming in for: \"I want\nto extend it this way."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 700050,
    "dDurationMs": 1527,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I want to hook into this, hook into this.\""
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 701577,
    "dDurationMs": 2946,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so he built a super\nextensive hook system."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 705630,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "MCP, obviously, this is a\nreally great extension point."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 708840,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and now there's slash\ncommands and subagents."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 711660,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And user-defined slash commands"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 713280,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is something we've invested in a lot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 715200,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the idea is it's just a workflow:"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 716970,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's like a markdown file."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 717900,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You put it in your code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 719250,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it's something that\nyou can reuse a lot."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 721410,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So for example,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 723180,
    "dDurationMs": 4710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I have a slash command for making commits."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 727890,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I have some instructions in there:"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 729630,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "here's how you write a good git commit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 731310,
    "dDurationMs": 2550,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I pre-allow the git commit Bash command"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 733860,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so I don't have to accept it every time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 736530,
    "dDurationMs": 1450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the model can just do it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 739620,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I think slash commands\nare really interesting,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 741210,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and agents are kind of a\ndifferent view of slash commands."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 743940,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, it's like a slash command,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 745680,
    "dDurationMs": 2613,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but it has a forked context window."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 749190,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so you can kind of think\nof agents and slash commands"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 751080,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as two sides of the same thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 753360,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this is also very exciting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 754530,
    "dDurationMs": 2708,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's just another way\nto extend Claude Code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 757238,
    "dDurationMs": 1582,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so when I look at the future,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 758820,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think a lot of it is just about"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 760380,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like how do we extend Claude Code more?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 763350,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How do we make it easier for\nother people to build on top?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 766110,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "How do we make the SDK\nmore useful for people?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 768210,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So it's useful for code if you\nwant to build a coding agent,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 771360,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also you can use it for other stuff."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 772650,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, anything that you need an agent for,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 774630,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can just use the SDK for."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 776640,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think these are the things"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 778350,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I'm the most excited about."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 779490,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And obviously all of this benefits"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 780780,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from all the other work we're doing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 782250,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to make the model more autonomous,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 783540,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to make it work for\nlonger periods of time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 785730,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to make it better adhere to instructions,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 787350,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to make it remember things better."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 789180,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so everything along\nthe way it benefits."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 791190,
    "dDurationMs": 2280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- So I'm using Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 793470,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or whatever form of it,\nin six to 12 months;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 797040,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what does my work actually look like?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 799680,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Am I reviewing PRs all day,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 802080,
    "dDurationMs": 3753,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or what does it day to day break down to?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 807240,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think there's gonna be a mix"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 808560,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of more hands-on coding."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 810930,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't think that's going away."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 812340,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And maybe it'll look different, though."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 814080,
    "dDurationMs": 1320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So maybe hands-on coding today"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 815400,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is directly manipulating text,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 817530,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but in the future it might be using Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 819600,
    "dDurationMs": 1743,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to manipulate the text for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 822240,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then I think there's\ngonna be this other bucket"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 823830,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of maybe less direct coding"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 826170,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where Claude proactively does something,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 828990,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and maybe Claude even reviewed it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 831600,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it's your job to\ndecide if this is a change"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 833910,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that you want or not."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 836040,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think maybe 12 or 24 months from now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 839820,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we're gonna start seeing\nClaude that's more about goals"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 842580,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and more about these higher\nlevel things that it needs to do"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 847260,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and less about the specific\ntasks that go into it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 849930,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The same way that, as an engineer,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 851520,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think about what is it that I want to do"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 853650,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "over the next month."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 854483,
    "dDurationMs": 2947,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I kind of make small\nchanges to work towards that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 857430,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Maybe Claude will go\nthrough the same thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 859800,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Right, sort moving up and\nup the stack, to some degree,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 862920,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of these like abstraction\nlevels of getting Claude"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 865800,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to make individual changes to files,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 867450,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to getting Claude to make\nchanges to a whole PR,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 870210,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to getting Claude to think\nabout a goal of building an app"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 873810,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or whatever else it is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 875670,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah.\n- Okay."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 877170,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's interesting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 878370,
    "dDurationMs": 2000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If I'm an engineer and I'm hearing that,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 881490,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it seems like there's\ngonna be a lot changing"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 884490,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a very short amount of time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 886020,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially with my role\nand what I should be doing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 889110,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What's your advice for folks out there"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 891120,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that are looking to prepare themselves"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 892920,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and adapt to this world?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 893910,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about what they should be learning"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 895260,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or what skills they should be developing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 897090,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- I think back to when I\nfirst started learning coding;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 900330,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I was the kid that sat in the back"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 902430,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of math class in middle school,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 904020,
    "dDurationMs": 3450,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I had my little TI-83 Plus calculator."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 907470,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It was like a transparent gray one;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 909870,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can kind of see the circuit."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 911970,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we just program it with BASIC,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 914850,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because at some point I realized that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 916860,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I can actually program the answers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 918600,
    "dDurationMs": 2350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for the math test into the calculator ."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 921870,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you can get better grades that way."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 924000,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 926400,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there's just something about\nkind of this visceral feeling"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 929190,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of being able to hack,\nand having this idea"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 931500,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of maybe there's this\none program I can make;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 933270,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just I go into my\ncalculator and I code it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 934950,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then I can just restart\nand use it really quick:"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 937080,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this kind of feedback cycle\nthat was really amazing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 939600,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it made it possible\nfor me to build stuff"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 941970,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that I never could have before."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 944130,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it was just so easy to get started."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 947190,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think about the difference"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 950010,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between that world and the\nworld before agentic coding,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 953940,
    "dDurationMs": 3873,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where stacks just got\nway, way too complicated."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 958650,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You know, if I wanted\nto make a JavaScript,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 960840,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, like website,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 962130,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I had to learn about\nReact and maybe Next.js,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 965190,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then three different build\nsystems and a deploy system."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 968250,
    "dDurationMs": 2073,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it was just so complicated."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 971310,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think one really\ncool thing about agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 973890,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that they're changing this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 975630,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So with coding agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 977550,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it makes it really easy to get started."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 979290,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And if you have an idea\nyou can just build it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 981390,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And it's a lot more about the idea now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 983580,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "than it is about the details,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 984960,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "because just like Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 987180,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can rewrite the code over and over."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 989070,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And, you know, Claude Code\nitself, we rewrite all the time."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 990990,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think this is just something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 992580,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that coding agents enable."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 994680,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The code itself is no longer precious."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 996990,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And there's still an art to writing it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 998940,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and, you know, all stone\ncode by hand sometimes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1001580,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And one of the engineers\non the team, Lena,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1003440,
    "dDurationMs": 1680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "she was talking about how on the weekends"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1005120,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "she still sometimes writes C++ by hand,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1007520,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just 'cause it's fun."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1009230,
    "dDurationMs": 2040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And, you know, as a coder,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1011270,
    "dDurationMs": 2163,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it can be a really\njoyous thing to do this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1014270,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But I think more and more"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1015103,
    "dDurationMs": 1747,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's gonna be about the thing you make"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1016850,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and not about the process\nof making it as much."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1020120,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I think my advice for\npeople learning to code today"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1024560,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is you still have to learn the craft."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1027560,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So you still have to learn\nto code, learn languages,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1029750,
    "dDurationMs": 3510,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "learn compilers, runtimes,\nhow to build web apps,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1033260,
    "dDurationMs": 1323,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how to build programs,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1035630,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "system design."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1036463,
    "dDurationMs": 1687,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You still have to know all the stuff,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1038150,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but also just start to get more creative."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1042080,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And, you know, if you\nhave an idea for a startup"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1043910,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or an idea for a product,\nyou can just build it now"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1046070,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a way that you just couldn't before."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1047810,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And we don't really\nunderstand what this means,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1049580,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but there's just so much potential"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1051890,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's about to be unlocked because of it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1053720,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I love that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1055640,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think that's great advice too."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1057260,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ideas suddenly become\nsomething you can action on in,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1061220,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you know, a span of a few minutes almost;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1064280,
    "dDurationMs": 3063,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whereas before it could be\njust in your backlog forever."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1069350,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Before we wrap, I want to ask you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1072260,
    "dDurationMs": 1860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as the creator of Claude Code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1074120,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what are your best practices\nfor using Claude Code?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1076730,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And any tips or tricks."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1078620,
    "dDurationMs": 3046,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- Yeah, I think the biggest\nthing that I recommend,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1081666,
    "dDurationMs": 2024,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "okay, maybe two tricks."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1083690,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So one thing I recommend"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1084800,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is that if you're brand new to Claude Code"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1086810,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you haven't used it before,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1088640,
    "dDurationMs": 1353,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "don't use it to write code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1093860,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I know it sounds crazy.\n- Yeah, explain, explain."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1095630,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "- But you gotta stop yourself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1096590,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Like, don't use it to write code yet."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1098570,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The thing to start with\nis use it to ask questions"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1100760,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "about the code base."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1102410,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So you can ask, you\nknow, if I want to make,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1104990,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "if I want to add a new\nlogger, how do I do that?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1107330,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then ask Claude Code\nto explore the code base"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1109670,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and figure it out for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1111170,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or why is this function\ndesigned the way that it is?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1115070,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Claude Code can go in and it\ncan look through Git history"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1117920,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it can answer this stuff for you."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1120320,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I think ask Claude Code\nquestions about the code base"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1122660,
    "dDurationMs": 1230,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just don't code yet."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1123890,
    "dDurationMs": 960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then once you feel comfortable"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1124850,
    "dDurationMs": 1740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with using Claude Code this way"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1126590,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and you get comfortable\nwith this idea of an agent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1128480,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's doing this research for you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1130310,
    "dDurationMs": 2223,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then start to use it to code."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1133730,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I think the second thing is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1134750,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when you are using Claude\nCode to write code,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1137750,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "think about what kind of\nwork do you want to do"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1140000,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and like how big is the task?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1141920,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So for something that's really easy,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1143930,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I kind of, in my mind,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1145280,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I have these three categories:"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1146270,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "easy, medium, and hard, very roughly."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1148580,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so easy tasks are something"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1149690,
    "dDurationMs": 1350,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that Claude can write in one shot;"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1151040,
    "dDurationMs": 2340,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "like one prompt, it'll\nget it pretty much right."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1153380,
    "dDurationMs": 1770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And nowadays I'll just go to GitHub"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1155150,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'll tag @Claude on an issue"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1156950,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and just have Claude write the PR for me."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1158840,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this is how I do easy tasks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1160220,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "'cause that frees up my terminal."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1161240,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't have to kind of spend it on this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1163940,
    "dDurationMs": 2310,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Medium tasks, I'll start\nit in the terminal,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1166250,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'll start in plan mode."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1167900,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So just Shift + Tab into plan,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1169340,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I'll align on a\nplan with Claude first."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1172220,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then once I feel good about the plan,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1174620,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'll go into auto-accept and\nI'll have it implemented."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1177350,
    "dDurationMs": 1260,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then for really hard tasks,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1178610,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm still the one driving,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1179750,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and Claude is more of a tool."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1181400,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And I'm kind of pairing with it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1183020,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But really I'm the one\nin the driver's seat,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1184610,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "not Claude for this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1186110,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so I'll use Claude maybe\nto do some code-based research,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1189770,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe prototype a few ideas,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1191420,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe I'll just like\nvibe code a few options"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1193610,
    "dDurationMs": 1710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to understand the boundaries of the system"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 1195320,
    "dDurationMs": 1410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and what works well."
    } ]
  }, {
